Changelog
=========

## 1.1.0 - 2020-04-10

 * Filter out nameless authors (Taeber Rapczak)
 * Update recent publication data for April 2020 (Taeber Rapczak)
 * Add link to data snapshots (Taeber Rapczak)

## 1.0.0 - 2020-03-17

 * Attribute data from Metabolomics Tools Wiki (Taeber Rapczak)
 * Reformat code in help.html (Taeber Rapczak)
 * Add favicon from main site (Taeber Rapczak)
 * Make slider arrows tab-focusable for accessibility (Taeber Rapczak)
 * Widen the widgets and make them mobile-friendly (Taeber Rapczak)
 * Cleanup dashboard script and switch to full publication date (Taeber Rapczak)
 * Add http-server as dev requirement (Taeber Rapczak)
 * Add missing `date` reference (Taeber Rapczak)
 * Remove images for old widgets (Taeber Rapczak)


## 0.5.0 - 2020-03-11

 * Rewrite Publications Listing script to improve UX (Taeber Rapczak)
 * Rework Person Listing to reduce network calls (Hunter Jarrell)
 * Update README with new Quickstart instructions (Taeber Rapczak)
 * Replace dashboard page widgets (Samantha Emerson)
 * Move parseVIVOString to entity module (Taeber Rapczak)
 * Update TPF client and other dependencies from upstream (Taeber Rapczak)


## 0.4.0 - 2020-02-27

 * Optimize page loading for Publications Listing (Taeber Rapczak)
 * Fix broken organization nesting (Taeber Rapczak)
 * Optimize page loading for Organization Listing (Taeber Rapczak)
 * Update copyright year 2020 (Taeber Rapczak)
 * Use new ontology properties: directs, directedBy (Taeber Rapczak)
 * Replace email with GitHub issue reporting link (Taeber Rapczak)
 * Use proper casing for Metabolomics Workbench (Taeber Rapczak)
 * Add Help link to Profile pages and fix menu (Taeber Rapczak)
 * Add Help page (Kevin Hanson)


## 0.3.0 - 2020-01-22

 * Reinterpret datasets to mean samples and analyses (Taeber Rapczak)
 * Remove links to non-existent datasets.html (Taeber Rapczak)
 * Fix links for bubbles (Taeber Rapczak)


## 0.2.1 - 2019-12-11

Fix sub-header menu link rewrite bug (Taeber Rapczak)


